"{\"uid\": \"binnews.com-content-2024-08-01-simone-biles-wins-gold-in-individual-all-around-final-at-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Photo:Getty Images  Gymnastics starSimone Bilesis adding another Olympic gold medal to her collection.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Thursday (August 1), Biles, 27, won gold in the women's gymnastics individual all-around final at the2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 213, \"end\": 227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles dazzled in the vault event before a form break in uneven bars earned her a sizeable deduction on her score.\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Biles made a big comeback on the balance beam and floor, where she performed the world's most difficult routine.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The gymnastic star faced stiff competition as she was up against fellow Team USA member and defending gold medalist of the individual all-aroundSuni Lee,who secured a bronze medal on Thursday.\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 539, \"end\": 547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.8756213115408032, \"rank\": 0.1398664352741316, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9997921570000332, \"rank\": 0.00011294320367346078, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q